{"tid":2361221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回憶小子快入]三美資行提早終止共484隻衍生產品 涉美國禁令","createTime":"2021-01-10T12:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T11:49:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d80e0300f31341c0f712cded789f07ffd51736","tid":2361221,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1610281227043&amp;issue=20210110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1610281227043%26issue%3D20210110&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7QoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=3b37ea5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1610281227043&amp;issue=20210110</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因應美國總統特朗普早前簽署的行政命令，禁止美國投資多間與中國軍方有關的企業，3間美資金融服務機構先後公布，提早終止共484隻衍生產品的的買賣。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通將暫停41隻與恒指相關的窩輪、11隻與國指相關的窩輪、5隻與恒指相關的界內證、三大中資電訊商共13隻窩輪、144隻恒指牛證、11隻國指牛熊證。1月25日起暫停買賣。<br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利將提早終止72隻跟恒指牛證、32隻恒指窩輪、以及11隻跟中移動（0941）有關的窩輪。1月25日起暫停買賣。<br />\n<br />\n高盛亦公布暫停買賣6隻跟中移動有關及3隻跟聯通（0762）有關的窩輪、13隻與恒指相關的窩輪，以及122隻與恒指牛證。1月25日起暫停買賣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人低位入咗941<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2353840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2353840</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入啦，快d入呀"},{"pid":"bdb4e1fb2e7ccfc4435488d318a2e41b6707228f","tid":2361221,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"回憶狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa48d6f651b5b339471e889ab6e6931b3d28786","tid":2361221,"uid":179729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"狗回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b93b2068828f760c0812de0e69298df426fd99","tid":2361221,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:18:57.000Z","ms